This recipie is great, but be careful to follow the instructions regarding pounding the chicken- you really don't want the breasts to be too thick, it will mean they will need to sautée longer than the ideal, making them dry. Also be careful about cleaning the saucepan out in between chicken batches- the pan will dry out and get crusty, & if you try to add more butter the chicken will become very greasy as well.

