I've made this recipe several times and it's very good. However, I modified it slightly to how I prepare it now. I use 3/4 cup of chicken stock instead of reduced broth and only 1/2 a cup of cream. Not a dramatic reduction in the cream the recipe calls for, but it lets the great flavors come through so much more. It's a good go-to recipe that I prepare about maybe 2-3 times a month. Very good to begin with, but IMO the slight tweaks I made have made it a bit better.

